      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's a different approach—it uses formal logic rules alongside neural networks, so it's supposed to be much more mathematically precise and eliminate the 'hallucinations' or weird cultural errors that LLMs sometimes have. Management thinks it'll be a lot more reliable for legal and technical docs.",
